As the market for used cooking oil continues to expand, competitive dynamics among key players like Pelican BioThermal LLC are expected to intensify. Companies are likely to focus on enhancing their collection and processing capabilities, leveraging technological advancements to improve efficiency and sustainability. Strategic partnerships and collaborations with stakeholders across the value chain will also be crucial for market players to strengthen their market position and expand their reach. Moreover, investments in research and development to explore new applications and value-added products derived from used cooking oil can provide opportunities for differentiation and growth in the increasingly competitive market landscape.

